79
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:28,601
And it's true that his elder had for so long been accepted by him as his ideal that all his young strength and energy could not but turn toward the ideal, even to the forgetting at that moment of everyone and everything, when his ideal elder is dying or dead, I guess, at this point.

80
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:41,801
