112
00:11:21,601 --> 00:11:31,041
Remember, in the background is Dostoevsky constantly showing you how different, how people influence and corrupt and help each other.

113
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,281
And Yvonne has corrupted him.

114
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,161
So the top of 390.

115
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:43,961
I will not forget, however, forget to mention something strange, which for a time came to the surface of Alyasha's mind at this fatal moment.

116
00:11:43,961 --> 00:11:50,760
This new something was the harassing impression left by the conversation with Yvonne, which now persistently haunted Alyasha.

117
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,361
At this moment, it haunted him.

118
00:11:52,361 --> 00:12:00,601
Well, it was not that something of fundamental, elemental, so to speak, faith of his soul, it's not that the faith of his soul had been shaken.

119
00:12:00,601 --> 00:12:06,520
He loved his God and firmly believed in him, though he was suddenly murmuring against him.

120
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:10,920
Remember, Yvonne says, I believe in God, or at least it doesn't matter whether you believe in God.

121
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:13,241
The question is whether you accept his world.

122
00:12:13,241 --> 00:12:19,481
And now he have, you know, faith, and Alyasha is beginning to lose his.

123
00:12:19,481 --> 00:12:28,681
A vague but tormenting and evil impression left by his conversation with Yvonne the day before revived again in his soul and seemed forcing its way to the surface.

124
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:40,760
So Yvonne has fed him up for having this rebellion reaction to the decomposition of Zosima, which is a special case of the general principle.

125
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:45,641
When you're in a spiritual crisis, you need miracles.

126
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:56,921
And Alyasha is in a spiritual crisis because his beloved monk is dying, has died, and is decomposing, and he needs a miracle, and he isn't getting it.

127
00:12:56,921 --> 00:13:02,841
At that moment, he's very close to losing his faith.

128
00:13:02,841 --> 00:13:05,481
And guess who arrives on the scene?

129
00:13:05,481 --> 00:13:08,401
Exactly at that moment.

130
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,601
On 391.

131
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:19,040
