133
00:13:20,481 --> 00:13:36,561
So Alyasha has thrown himself on the ground in despair, really, that this person whom he loves and who's the unconditional commitment of his life isn't being recognized by the universe or by God as he should be.

134
00:13:36,561 --> 00:13:46,481
