153
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:20,040
Let me just make sure I am where I want to be.

154
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:20,760
Yeah.

155
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,840
So, anybody want to say anything?

156
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:28,840
